IZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:40:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bba43123f1b3c3d57f8decd7984b23895e1eacde","tid":1191922,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:40:57.000Z","msg":"要對抗三毛分化技倆，首先自己要先拚棄批評其他同路人所做出嘅行為，同路人係指任何反共力量（包括泛民），而唔包括返工不了/ 遊行有乜用？（消極撚）/ 散播負面情緒嘅分化撚三毛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n假設如果你想衝但面對人地係和理非嘅立場，唔好鬧人，相反如果你係和理非但面對人地係想衝嘅立場，亦都唔好鬧人甚至阻人，否則會破壞大家關係從而削弱反共力量<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再強調一次，要杜絕三毛分化，首先自己要先拚棄批評其他同路人所做出嘅行為，至於唔同門派之間嘅舊仇恨，宜家大敵當前兵臨城下，都唔好互踩住（eg黃毓民、陳雲甚至熱狗之流，雖然我都覺得熱狗好賤格，但只要冇人彩佢無視佢就可以，冇必要鬧戰）否則三毛好易利用呢點製造缺口挑撥「土本vs泛民」嘅關係，造成反共力量嘅內亂。呢條守則任何反共力量（包括泛民&amp;本土）都應該要守<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6月9號！大家一齊上街！"},{"pid":"720854549d80de1aaba77fff46aa984721fedbe1","tid":1191922,"uid":35094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e92de321f1786c4613bf3869b5d87cbe16b0a591","tid":1191922,"uid":199957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dda3c4c8df2575da3fa18c49daacf29062babb9f","tid":1191922,"uid":136151,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:48:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gDm3jZc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgDm3jZc.png&h=c4afdae0&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:40:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:42:53.000Z","msg":"幅圖真係越睇越正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a28bc395b8d6706383ac986510f15bdda3fcdcc","tid":1191922,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislik